She watched as Quickstrike stepped away from her.  She closed her 
eyes. She took a deep breath and re-opened her eyes. She took her 
hand and pulled the pelt up closer to her chin. She 
whispered,"Commander, don't you know me, DarkMouse, your subordinant?
She coughed a bit and looked at him. "Have you gotten megatron back 
yet for sending us on a fools errend yet?"
She coughed and pulled at the pelt.
